ce-Aaronson.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杰西·乔·斯塔克身着雪儿的鲍勃·麦基复古服装。图片来源：雷斯·阿伦森" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jesse-Jo-Star-in-Chers-vintage-Bob-Mackie-costume.-Credit_-Rayce-Aaronson.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jesse-Jo-Star-in-Chers-vintage-Bob-Mackie-costume.-Credit_-Rayce-Aaronson-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jesse-Jo-Star-in-Chers-vintage-Bob-Mackie-costume.-Credit_-Rayce-Aaronson-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jesse-Jo-Star-in-Chers-vintage-Bob-Mackie-costume.-Credit_-Rayce-Aaronson-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jesse-Jo-Star-in-Chers-vintage-Bob-Mackie-costume.-Credit_-Rayce-Aaronson-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jesse-Jo-Star-in-Chers-vintage-Bob-Mackie-costume.-Credit_-Rayce-Aaronson-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/jesse-jo-stark">杰西·乔·斯塔克 (Jesse Jo Stark)</a>在拉斯维加斯表演时穿着雪儿 ( <a href="/artists/cher">Cher</a> ) 的一套复古服装，以时尚的方式迎接新年。</p><p>这位歌手在她的 Instagram 官方页面上分享了自己在闪闪发光的乐团中摆姿势和表演的照片。这套服装是 70 年代末鲍勃·麦基 (Bob Mackie) 的复古单品，雪儿 (Cher) 本人（恰好是斯塔克的教母）穿过，是她个人档案的一部分。这件作品忠实于斯塔克标志性的渔网和缠腰布表演风格。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C1m3y-wRZmi/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-conten